Building statically linked VST Plugin:
======================================

Install devel tools:

$ xcode-select --install

You also need these brew packages

$ brew install autoconf-archive automake ccache libao pkg-config libtool gtk-doc

Finally: edit macos/sdk-options.sh

$ cd macos
$ ./build-deps.sh
$ ./build.sh

Build cross compiled version:

$ cd macos
$ ./clean-rebuild.sh # nodeps
